  "3169520": {
    "name": "Warhammer 40,000: Space Marine - Master Crafted Edition",
    "steam_appid": 3169520,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Warhammer 40,000: Space Marine》回归。专为新世代强化归来！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经过优化的游戏体验与画质效果，让《Warhammer 40,000: Space Marine》的游玩体验更上一层楼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >优化内容：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >材质优化与保真度提升 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4k 分辨率</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色模型优化 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >界面焕新 + 现代化操控方案</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >音频重制</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >产品概述</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿上所向披靡的星际战士装甲，结合使用多种致命武器，碾碎数目庞大的欧克大军。沉浸于紧张刺激而又暴力野蛮的世界之中，遨游有史以来设定最为丰富的科学奇幻宇宙。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169520/extras/89366f3c27cdb2b58bcb457098947dca.webp?t=1763648701\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169520/extras/89366f3c27cdb2b58bcb457098947dca.poster.avif?t=1763648701\" class=\"bb_img\" width=612 height=346 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Warhammer 40,000: Space Marine》中，你是泰特斯上尉，一名分属于极限战士团的星际战士。你身经百战，久经沙场。不计其数的欧克组成的强大部落已然侵入了一座帝国铸造世界——那是一座行星大小的制造工厂，专为人类永无止境的生存之战制造各式武器。这颗星球绝不能落入敌手，可在这个世界的阴影之中还潜藏着更加黑暗邪恶的威胁。一支帝国解放舰队已在途中，极限战士团受命先行进入，坚守关键阵地直至援军抵达。手执爆矢枪、挥舞链锯剑，泰特斯上尉将与极限战士团的老兵一道向人类之敌发起猛攻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Warhammer 40,000: Space Marine – Master Crafted Edition》包含原版《星际战士》游戏本体，以及已发布的所有DLC：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• Chaos Unleashed Map Pack</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• Dreadnought Assault DLC</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• Iron Hand Veteran Chapter Pack DLC</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• Death Guard Champion Chapter Pack DLC</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• Golden Relic Bolter</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• Golden Relic Chainsword</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• Power Sword</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• Blood Angels Veteran Armour Set</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• Salamanders Veteran Armour Set</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• Alpha Legion Champion Armour Set</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• Legion of the Damned Armour Set</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• Emperor's Elite Pack</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• Traitor Legions Pack</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如暴风席卷战场。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >化身势不可挡的星际战士，无所畏惧、直面最激烈的战斗。无需躲藏、永不退缩，斩杀一切挡路之敌。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169520/extras/1ad7908442c13c782cbf43c25f270fa9.webp?t=1763648701\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169520/extras/1ad7908442c13c782cbf43c25f270fa9.poster.avif?t=1763648701\" class=\"bb_img\" width=612 height=346 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >血腥残暴的杀戮。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >运用创新性的战斗系统，无缝切换大口径的远程武器与毁灭性的近身打击。消灭敌人的感觉从未如此酣畅淋漓。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169520/extras/27f99f0ae25c423e2e2d50cba023b861.webp?t=1763648701\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169520/extras/27f99f0ae25c423e2e2d50cba023b861.poster.avif?t=1763648701\" class=\"bb_img\" width=612 height=346 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与队友在线对战。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组建你自己的星际战士小队或混沌星际战士团，参加 8 vs 8 在线匹配对战。获取经验值，解锁全新武器和装甲，自定义毁灭者、突击兵和战术兵等星际战士职业。支持跨平台游戏功能</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169520/extras/2a34e5e9c8444b4cbf3d10c1f1286fbd.webp?t=1763648701\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169520/extras/2a34e5e9c8444b4cbf3d10c1f1286fbd.poster.avif?t=1763648701\" class=\"bb_img\" width=612 height=346 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验《战锤40k》的残酷黑暗。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >投身于这个宏伟的宇宙，见证壮丽的景观、致命的敌人、庞大的战役和无情的毁灭。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169520/extras/07674c5ac7a43c7f4fff869c4076ecc9.webp?t=1763648701\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169520/extras/07674c5ac7a43c7f4fff869c4076ecc9.poster.avif?t=1763648701\" class=\"bb_img\" width=612 height=346 /></picture></span></p>",
